With over 3.5 million articles,chances are wikipedia has the answer to many of your questions.
You need to search to find them.It makes no sense to Google wikipedia articles.We have redesigned
wikipedia's search experience in Xhtml and CSS.We have not made any api calls so the page is static.
Contribute and let's make wikipedia the next big thing in Search engines.Go to 
http://wikipedia.oasiswebsoft.com/ to view the web page.